summary: I am a software developer (PHP mostly) who loves architecture. Software that "works" is not my passion; conceptually sound software that "works" is. I have a special love for lean software architectures that can achieve their goal without using or exposing privacy sensitive information. I currently spend most of my time in the WordPress space. I am co-founder of admincolumns.com, which is created by an amazing (fun) team.
